Season: 2000

Oceanian Nations Cup 2000

Results
Details
Squad lists
Results

Melanesian Cup and Polynesian Cup tournaments have been used as 
qualifiers for the 2000 Oceania Nations Cup, with teams finishing 
first and second winning the right to progress to the Final Tournament,
in Tahiti. 

